10 WHEREAS, the dedication, sportsmanship, and teamwork demonstrated by the St.
11 Louis Catholic Saints reflect great credit upon the players, coaches, faculty, families, and the
12 entire Lake Charles community.
13 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
14 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend and congratulate the St. Louis Catholic High
15 School boys soccer team upon winning the Division III state championship and does hereby
16 extend best wishes for continued success in the future.
17 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to St.
18 Louis Catholic High School and to head coach Zach Malik.
